{"ts":"2026-06-26T06:09:53.094Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Developing the Build Blueprint**\n\nI'm now iterating on the interactive `/build/blueprint` tool. I'm visualizing the core sections: the interactive readiness assessment preview with dynamic dashboards, solution recommendations in a bento-grid, and the 90-day sovereign roadmap as an editorial timeline with visual progress. I'm also preparing a compelling call to action to launch a custom blueprint evaluation.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T06:09:55.016Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Defining the Marketplace**\n\nI'm now revising the `/platforms/marketplace` concept, clarifying its purpose. It's not an e-commerce platform. Instead, this curated registry presents pre-audited agent patterns and accelerators for deployment, focusing on security and custom cognitive additions. I am envisioning a neural accelerator registry layout that focuses on usability, with an interactive filter system, detail drawers, and a deployment lifecycle visualization. The hero will be updated with a badge and a visual module network.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T06:09:57.004Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Refining the Marketplace**\n\nI'm now diving deeper into the marketplace design. I envision an interactive filtering system that will allow users to quickly filter and explore enterprise accelerators by specific categories. Each accelerator card will feature interactive options such as \"Inspect Schema\" or \"Sandbox Deploy\". I am focusing on creating a custom SVG/CSS architecture block to explain the function of each accelerator, and a premium call to action to discuss deployment within their secure network. I'm also planning the narrative for the Control Center, to highlight its importance in deploying, maintaining, tracking spend, governing access, and monitoring.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T06:09:58.458Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Visualizing the Control Hub**\n\nI'm now iterating on the visual metaphor for the executive operation dashboard and governance command console. I am focusing on developing the layout strategy. I'm focusing on the \"Delivery Operations & Control\" category, with the deep dark dashboard header. I'm developing a beautifully rotating SVG 3D-like control hub visual. I'm now developing Section 1: The Control Cockpit Preview, with three sub-interfaces.\n\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
