{"ts":"2026-06-26T06:11:14.148Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Evaluating Component Perfection**\n\nI've determined this component is essentially perfect as is, including all necessary elements such as the header, footer, and animated background. My focus has now shifted to inspecting other subpages and ensuring seamless navigation, specifically linking them within the platforms hub. I am currently considering how to make the platforms hub more accessible.\n\n\n**Considering Platform Connections**\n\nI'm now contemplating how to integrate the newly designated premium enterprise pages: `/platforms/blueprint`, `/platforms/marketplace`, and `/platforms/control-center`. My current goal is to determine the best approach, whether to add references or cards linking these pages on the platforms hub. I'm reviewing if these are referenced on the platforms hub already.\n\n\n**Refining Platform Architecture**\n\nI'm now diving deeper into the `/platforms` architecture. I'm prioritizing the design of `/platforms/blueprint/page.tsx` and verifying the necessary subdirectories for these premium offerings. I have confirmed that `/platforms/marketplace` is linked in the Footer, as well as InteractiveExperienceSection, and JourneySection. I am considering refining `/platforms` to offer a designer-grade platforms overview that integrates `Blueprint`, `Marketplace`, and `Control Center`.\n\n\n**Developing Blueprint Structure**\n\nI'm now focused on fleshing out `/platforms/blueprint/page.tsx`, and making it exceptional. My priorities include developing a custom readiness scoring dashboard with interactive components to showcase assessment areas and GFF maturity metrics. I also need to craft a solution recommendations section using custom UI elements. I'm ensuring this has a unique editorial feel. I am checking the other pages, but believe this one needs focus.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T06:11:14.153Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"1uz4mm56","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/platforms/blueprint/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport { useState } from \"react\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\nimport { \n  Compass, \n  ShieldCheck, \n  Database, \n  Cpu, \n  Network, \n  Clock, \n  TrendingUp, \n  ArrowRight, \n  CheckCircle2, \n  Gauge, \n  Sliders, \n  AlertCircle \n} from \"lucide-react\";\nimport InnerPageShell from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageShell\";\nimport InnerPageHero from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageHero\";\nimport MotionReveal from \"@/components/inner-pages/MotionReveal\";\nimport { BentoGrid, BentoCard } from \"@/components/inner-pages/BentoGrid\";\nimport PremiumCTA from \"@/components/inner-pages/PremiumCTA\";\n\n// Readiness Audit Dimensions\nconst AUDIT_DIMENSIONS = [\n  {\n    id: \"governance\",\n    title: \"Governance & Security\",\n    score: 84,\n    level: \"Operational but Unmanaged\",\n    icon: ShieldCheck,\n    color: \"blue\",\n    gap: \"Fragmented security checks without automated kernel logs (eBPF). Token safety policies are applied at proxy level rather than container-level sandboxing.\",\n    target: \"Deploy custom Sovereign Guardrail policies with zero-trust eBPF telemetry and real-time PII masking before agent routing.\",\n    tech: [\"eBPF Shield\", \"Guardrail Policy Engine\", \"PII Redaction Core\"]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"data\",\n    title: \"Data Surface Density\",\n    score: 42,\n    level: \"Siloed & Unstructured\",\n    icon: Database,\n    color: \"red\",\n    gap: \"Corporate intellectual property is locked across disconnected departments (legacy CSVs, internal wiki pages, SQL tables) with no unified vector-graph mesh.\",\n    target: \"Orchestrate a sovereign hybrid vector-graph index using Neo4j and pgvector to offer low-latency, secure search across all internal data boundaries.\",\n    tech: [\"GFF Data Fabric\", \"Graph-Vector Mesh\", \"Neo4j / pgvector\"]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"compute\",\n    title: \"Compute Scalability\",\n    score: 65,\n    level: \"Elastic but Inefficient\",\n    icon: Cpu,\n    color: \"purple\",\n    gap: \"Compute workloads are statically provisioned on general Kubernetes nodes, leading to excessive token overhead and idle cluster costs during off-peak hours.\",\n    target: \"Implement dynamic SLA-based compute scaling that shifts resources dynamically between non-production containers and critical pipelines.\",\n    tech: [\"K8s Auto-scalers\", \"vLLM Multi-tenant Runtime\", \"SLA Node Manager\"]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"integration\",\n    title: \"Integration Surface\",\n    score: 55,\n    level: \"Ad-Hoc API Triggers\",\n    icon: Network,\n    color: \"blue\",\n    gap: \"Current business systems are invoked via legacy webhooks without deterministic idempotency or standard state recovery. Lack of reliable Human-in-the-Loop approval workflows.\",\n    target: \"Inject GFF Action Gateways running on Temporal with strict cryptographic ledger audits and idempotent state machines for outbound triggers.\",\n    tech: [\"Temporal Orchs\", \"Idempotent Webhooks\", \"Joint Cryptographic Audit\"]\n  }\n];\n\nexport default function BlueprintPage() {\n  const [activeDimId, setActiveDimId] = useState(\"data\");\n  const activeDim = AUDIT_DIMENSIONS.find((d) => d.id === activeDimId) || AUDIT_DIMENSIONS[0];\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Tier 0 • Diagnostics & Strategy\"\n        title=\"Enterprise AI Blueprints\"\n        highlightedWord=\"Blueprints\"\n        description=\"Audit existing data structures, analyze regulatory boundaries, and design mathematically structured multi-agent topologies before writing code.\"\n        breadcrumbs={[\n          { label: \"Platforms\", href: \"/platforms\" },\n          { label: \"Blueprint Strategy\" }\n        ]}\n      />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-24\">\n        \n        {/* Executive Summary Narrative */}\n        <MotionReveal className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 py-10 border-y border-white/5 items-center bg-white/[0.01] rounded-2xl px-6\">\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-5\">\n            <span className=\"text-xs font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold\">Strategic Framework</span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-2 tracking-tight\">The Diagnostic Foundation</h2>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-7\">\n            <p className=\"text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm\">\n              We believe successful enterprise AI is an architectural discipline, not a series of prompt engineering experiments. Before GFF deploys an agent, we model your entire system topology. By auditing your data surfaces, evaluating security parameters, and designing a deterministic roadmap, we convert executive goals into enterprise-grade sovereign software blueprints.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        {/* SECTION 1: Interactive Readiness Scoring Engine */}\n        <MotionReveal className=\"space-y-8\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n            <h2 className=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight\">Interactive Readiness Assessor</h2>\n            <p className=\"text-white/50 text-sm mt-2 font-light\">\n              Select any core architectural dimension below to inspect standard GFF readiness gaps and recommended targets.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto items-stretch\">\n            {/* Dimension Selection Column */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-3 justify-center\">\n              {AUDIT_DIMENSIONS.map((dim) => {\n                const Icon = dim.icon;\n                const isSelected = dim.id === activeDimId;\n                const colorTheme = dim.color === \"red\" ? \"text-red-400 border-red-500/30 bg-red-500/5\" : dim.color === \"purple\" ? \"text-purple-400 border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-500/5\" : \"text-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-[#009DFF]/5\";\n                \n                return (\n                  <button\n                    key={dim.id}\n                    onClick={() => setActiveDimId(dim.id)}\n                    className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition-all flex items-center justify-between group ${\n                      isSelected \n                        ? `${colorTheme} ring-1 ring-white/10` \n                        : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:bg-black/60 hover:border-white/10\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                      <Icon className={`w-5 h-5 ${isSelected ? \"\" : \"text-white/40 group-hover:text-white\"}`} />\n                      <div>\n                        <h4 className=\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\">{dim.title}</h4>\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase text-white/40 font-mono tracking-wider\">Level: {dim.level}</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"flex flex-col items-end\">\n                      <span className={`text-base font-mono font-bold ${dim.score < 50 ? \"text-red-400\" : dim.score < 75 ? \"text-yellow-400\" : \"text-emerald-400\"}`}>\n                        {dim.score}%\n                      </span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] uppercase text-white/30 tracking-widest\">Audit Score</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </button>\n                );\n              })}\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Inspection Detail Panel */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 bg-[#04060b] rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group\">\n              {/* Radial background ambient gradient based on active color */}\n              <div className={`absolute top-0 right-0 w-[50%] h-[50%] rounded-full blur-[60px] opacity-10 transition-all duration-500 ${\n                activeDim.color === \"red\" ? \"bg-red-500\" : activeDim.color === \"purple\" ? \"bg-purple-500\" : \"bg-[#009DFF]\"\n              }`} />\n\n              <div className=\"relative z-10 space-y-6\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                  <div>\n                    <span className=\"px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[9px] bg-white/5 text-white/60 border border-white/10 uppercase font-mono tracking-widest font-bold\">\n                      Readiness Inspector\n                    </span>\n                    <h3 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-1.5\">{activeDim.title} Analysis</h3>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Circular Dial Visual */}\n                  <div className=\"relative w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                    <svg className=\"w-full h-full transform -rotate-95\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\">\n                      <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"38\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.04)\" strokeWidth=\"6\" fill=\"none\" />\n                      <circle \n                        cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"38\" \n                        stroke={activeDim.color === \"red\" ? \"#EF4444\" : activeDim.color === \"purple\" ? \"#A855F7\" : \"#009DFF\"} \n                        strokeWidth=\"6\" \n                        fill=\"none\" \n                        strokeDasharray=\"239\" \n                        strokeDashoffset={239 - (239 * activeDim.score) / 100}\n                        strokeLinecap=\"round\"\n                        className=\"transition-all duration-1000 ease-out\"\n                      />\n                    </svg>\n                    <span className=\"absolute text-sm font-mono font-bold text-white\">{activeDim.score}%</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-red-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                      <AlertCircle className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> Identified Architecture Gap\n                    </div>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light\">{activeDim.gap}</p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-emerald-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                      <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> GFF Recommendation Target\n                    </div>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 leading-relaxed font-light\">{activeDim.target}</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"relative z-10 mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-3\">\n                <div className=\"flex flex-col\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] uppercase text-white/40 tracking-wider\">Diagnostic Modules</span>\n                  <div className=\"mt-1 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5\">\n                    {activeDim.tech.map((t, idx) => (\n                      <span key={idx} className=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-[4px] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-[9px] font-mono text-white/70\">\n                        {t}\n                      </span>\n                    ))}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <Link \n                  href=\"/build/blueprint\"\n                  className=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 text-xs font-semibold rounded-lg text-white border border-white/10 flex items-center gap-1.5 transition-all\"\n                >\n                  Configure Simulator <ArrowRight className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                </Link>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        {/* SECTION 2: Solution Recommendations & Expected Impact */}\n        <MotionReveal className=\"space-y-8\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n            <h2 className=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight\">Solution Topologies</h2>\n            <p className=\"text-white/50 text-sm mt-2 font-light\">\n              Hardened cognitive architectures designed to resolve systemic business friction.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <BentoGrid>\n            <BentoCard\n              title=\"Autonomous Compliance Core\"\n              description=\"Continuous eBPF kernel monitors scanning live database transactions, auto-redacting PII leaks and validating regulatory ledger schemas on-premise.\"\n              badge=\"Security Mesh\"\n              glowColor=\"red\"\n              metric={{ value: \"-98%\", label: \"PII Leakage Overhead\" }}\n            />\n            <BentoCard\n              title=\"Cognitive Pipeline Mesh\"\n              description=\"Sovereign multi-agent router connecting multi-modal models to parse complex regulatory compliance requests, compile departmental assets, and generate audit reports.\"\n              badge=\"Reasoning Loop\"\n              glowColor=\"blue\"\n              metric={{ value: \"10x\", label: \"Workload Speed Multiplier\" }}\n            />\n            <BentoCard\n              title=\"Action Gateway Network\"\n              description=\"Cryptographically signed outbound brokers executing idempotent operations in legacy SAP systems or SCADA control surfaces with human-approval gates.\"\n              badge=\"Deterministic Execution\"\n              glowColor=\"purple\"\n              metric={{ value: \"Zero-Risk\", label: \"State Recoverability\" }}\n            />\n          </BentoGrid>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        {/* SECTION 3: 90-Day Sovereign Roadmap */}\n        <MotionReveal className=\"space-y-12\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n            <h2 className=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight\">The 90-Day Sovereign Roadmap</h2>\n            <p className=\"text-white/50 text-sm mt-2 font-light\">\n              From initial readiness analysis to fully governed production clusters, designed with premium execution speed.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"relative max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n            {/* Timeline center line */}\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-[30px] md:left-1/2 w-[1px] bg-white/10\" />\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-12\">\n              {[\n                {\n                  phase: \"Phase 1\",\n                  days: \"Days 1–30\",\n                  title: \"Diagnostics & Topology Design\",\n                  desc: \"Conduct deep-dive workshops with stakeholders, compliance offices, and DevOps engineers. Run the GFF Readiness scoring engine to map data surfaces and secure sandbox boundaries.\",\n                  side: \"left\"\n                },\n                {\n                  phase: \"Phase 2\",\n                  days: \"Days 31–60\",\n                  title: \"Sandbox Prototype & DAG Coding\",\n                  desc: \"Establish local sandbox clusters inside the GFF Garage. Build multi-agent DAG pipelines inside GFF Foundry, load custom knowledge graphs, and test sandbox policy enforcement rules.\",\n                  side: \"right\"\n                },\n                {\n                  phase: \"Phase 3\",\n                  days: \"Days 61–90\",\n                  title: \"Cluster Scaling & Production Delivery\",\n                  desc: \"Promote validated sandbox agents into high-availability production clusters inside the GFF Factory layer. Connect live SAP, SCADA, or SQL streams and deploy the Control Center dashboard.\",\n                  side: \"left\"\n                }\n              ].map((step, idx) => (\n                <div key={idx} className={`relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start ${step.side === \"right\" ? \"md:flex-row-reverse\" : \"\"}`}>\n                  {/* Timeline point */}\n                  <div className=\"absolute left-[30px] md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-black border-2 border-[#009DFF] z-10 flex items-center justify-center\">\n                    <div className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\" />\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Spacer or empty side for desktop */}\n                  <div className=\"w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block\" />\n\n                  {/* Card Side */}\n                  <div className=\"w-full md:w-1/2 pl-12 md:pl-0 md:px-8\">\n                    <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-[#009DFF]/20 transition-all duration-300 relative group\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\">\n                          {step.phase}\n                        </span>\n                        <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">{step.days}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <h3 className=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight\">{step.title}</h3>\n                      <p className=\"mt-2 text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light group-hover:text-white/60 transition-colors\">\n                        {step.desc}\n                      </p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              ))}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        {/* CTA Section */}\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Ready to Code Your Strategic Blueprint?\"\n          description=\"Use our interactive, frontend-only Blueprint Generator tool to instantly scope model requirements, calculate compute budgets, and generate an enterprise topology diagram.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Launch Blueprint Generator\"\n          primaryHref=\"/build/blueprint\"\n        />\n\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}"}}}
